---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service | Winter Haven Concrete Contractors"
  description="Terms of service for Winter Haven Concrete Contractors. Read our terms and conditions for concrete services in Polk County, FL."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: February 2025</p>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          By accessing our website or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Winter Haven Concrete Contractors provides concrete installation and repair services including driveways, patios, slabs, and decorative concrete work. All services are subject to a written estimate and agreement before work begins.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Estimates and Pricing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          All estimates are provided free of charge and are valid for 30 days unless otherwise stated. Final pricing may vary based on:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Site conditions discovered during preparation</li>
          <li>Changes requested by the customer</li>
          <li>Material cost fluctuations</li>
          <li>Additional work beyond the original scope</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Payment Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Payment terms will be outlined in your service agreement. We accept cash, check, and major credit cards. A deposit may be required for larger projects.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Warranty</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          We stand behind our work with a satisfaction guarantee. Specific warranty terms will be provided in your service agreement. Warranties do not cover damage caused by improper use, natural disasters, or lack of maintenance.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Winter Haven Concrete Contractors shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid for the specific service giving rise to the claim.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Cancellation</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Cancellation policies vary by project. Please refer to your service agreement for specific cancellation terms and any applicable fees.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
          <strong>Winter Haven Concrete Contractors</strong><br>
          Phone: <a href="tel:+18633966145" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">(863) 396-6145</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
